data.description: Family Home, just blocks from Imperial Beach! This amazing property has plenty of living space and a multi-purpose room with a bedroom, full bath and separate entrance!  Great for entertaining and family gatherings!  Enjoy the beautiful new upgrades including new kitchen cabinets and quartz countertops, stainless steal appliances, new flooring, upgraded full hall bath, fresh interior paint throughout, new fixtures, refinished wood floors, exterior paint and new roll up garage door. Take a walk or bike ride to the IB Pier, a popular spot for strolling, pier fishing, watching the sunset, and sweeping views of the Los Coronados Islands.  Close to military bases, retail, restaurants, schools and freeway.
